            <title>[HBASE-4278] Race condition in Slab.java that occurs due to spinlock unlocking early</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4278</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Just a race condition in 4027. Occurs due to a spinlock that happens if the slab allocator is empty. When the slab allocator gets gets a slice of memory returned, if multiple threads are locked, both can be freed at the same time, leading one to throw an exception.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
